def multiplication_table(number, heading = '', decorate = false)
  output = heading.center(number * 4)
  output << "\n"
  output << '-' * number * 4
  output << "\n"
  number.times do |i|
    output << ' ' if decorate
    output << (i * number).to_s.rjust(3)
    output << ' |' if decorate
  end
  output << "\n"
  output << '-' * number * 4
  output << "\n"
  number.times do |i|
    number.times do |j|
      output << ' ' if decorate
      output << (i * j).to_s.rjust(3)
      output << ' |' if decorate
    end
    output << "\n"
  end
  output
end
